Titolo: Cross Racing Championship 2005

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Cross Racing Championship 2005 (CRC 2005) is a racing video game developed by Invictus Games and released on October 4, 2005 for Microsoft Windows. The Hungarian metal band SZEG contributed to the soundtrack. The game combines elements of rallycross with those of tuning. It was relaunched on September 18, 2018 as Cross Racing Championship Extreme in the Steam store.